Note: File I/O

Note: Write to a file
Write "Hello from EPL!" to file "output.txt"
Print "Wrote to output.txt"

Note: Append to the file
Append "This is line 2" to file "output.txt"
Append "This is line 3" to file "output.txt"
Print "Appended 2 lines"

Note: Read the file
content = Read file "output.txt"
Print "File contents:"
Print content
